-- ConvergeNet Says Its First-Half Net Income Declined by 48% to $2.6 Million
-- Paul Richardson
-- 2010-04-23T05:08:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/convergenet-says-its-first-half-net-income-declined-by-48-to-2-6-million.html

          
          
             ConvergeNet Holdings Ltd. said
first-half profit dropped to 19.5 million rand from 37.8 million
rand a year earlier.  
 The company commented in a statement published in the
Johannesburg-based Business Day newspaper today.  
          
          


  


        